{"tid":727691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺驚現污染血河","createTime":"2018-07-03T08:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T08:34:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9e4ff631f29beb558642f5ea0a6e6745cc45d8","tid":727691,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180703/large/03la4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180703%2Flarge%2F03la4p3.jpg&h=fe8ad4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有河流懷疑被大幅度污染，影響生態環境。有粉嶺的村民日前發現，隔開安樂村與崇謙堂村的一段麻芴河，日前被染了一片紅。「紅水」不單散發陣陣漂白水味，舀起時更會冒出白煙，關注團體認為是附近工廠擅自把工業原料倒進麻芴河而致，擔心情況若不受控，會進一步污染附近的梧桐河，令魚隻死亡。渠務署表示已派員了解及跟進事件，但拒絕透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有濃烈漂白水味</strong><br />\n<br />\n新界東民生關注組召集人方國珊表示，日前收到崇謙堂村村民投訴，指麻芴河數日前開始有大量「紅水」自渠口流出；到場觀察後發現，受污染河水異常鮮紅「有如血水」，估計面積達80平方米，「見到都驚」。她嘗試舀起一些「紅水」時，發現有些微白煙冒出，並帶有濃烈漂白水味。她指「最擔心係唔止污染呢條河，如果向北流去梧桐河，影響更大」。她會把「紅水」交予公開大學化驗，希望找出污染源頭。她亦已向上水警署報案，警方暫列作雜項事件處理。<br />\n<br />\n有網民亦在fb群組「North District北區」發帖指，上月30日經過安樂門街時，發現其中一座大廈有人嘗試「駁渠」把紅色污水排出。惟網民表示不確認是否麻芴河的污染源頭。據Google地圖資料，安樂門街有多間汽車維修中心、貨倉等。<br />\n<br />\n綠色力量總監鄭睦奇表示，據相片判斷，河水很有可能是因電鍍廠房產生的電鍍溶液和染料污染「變紅」；至於受污染的水會冒出白煙，則或代表水質受到揮發物質污染。他認為應盡快阻截河水進一步流至其他地方，以免生態受到更大破壞。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438544&d=Q9EuaZy05Qwl7heWc3LCF4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=43472fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438544&h=be703500\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438544</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/161740_a567b58b030d8cdccf5bbd8bbc4a4921.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F161740_a567b58b030d8cdccf5bbd8bbc4a4921.png&h=b0d11654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a07f8787deaf032ac32073fc6278d46f2be1288","tid":727691,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/162309_bf955a4c1f4867280ec14f40f8ad02b1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F162309_bf955a4c1f4867280ec14f40f8ad02b1.jpeg&h=c78fff1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d432ccf479097c4612b18b498a4edb6380e6c1c","tid":727691,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"女人黎m姐 大驚小怪"},{"pid":"2b82de4bce354bb197718f14a27840598b2ab865","tid":727691,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"大陸咩色都有啦<br />\n大驚小怪"},{"pid":"2275705fefc767e99e16304fa50f5b3648b43fd2","tid":727691,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a07f8787deaf032ac32073fc6278d46f2be1288","tid":727691,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/162309_bf955a4c1f4867280ec14f40f8ad02b1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F162309_bf955a4c1f4867280ec14f40f8ad02b1.jpeg&h=c78fff1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"成盤係血當佢無事 話知話知豬乸當佢係靚西施"},{"pid":"983d1735c95f5c90278770ccb3bd303e5fd507ae","tid":727691,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"滿江紅"}]}